videos.headline: Etienne erupts for a 59-yard TD
videos.description: Clemson RB Travis Etienne find a hole and burst for a 59-yard touchdown to put the Tigers up 7-0.

videos.headline: Clemson's Muse picks off Hartman
videos.description: Wake Forest QB Sam Hartman scrambles and throws a interception to Clemson's Tannner Muse.

videos.headline: Etienne's 4th-down conversion leads to TD
videos.description: On fourth down, Travis Etienne runs outside to give Clemson a first down and later scores a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Lawrence rips 55-yard TD pass
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence connects with a wide-open Justyn Ross for a 55-yard touchdown to put the Tigers up 21-0.

videos.headline: Clemson RB gallops in for his 3rd TD
videos.description: Clemson's Travis Etienne goes untouched for a 70-yard touchdown, his third score of the day.

videos.headline: Clemson RB escapes for a 65-yard TD
videos.description: Lyn-j Dixon gashes through the defense for a 65-yard Clemson touchdown.

videos.headline: Brice connects with a leaping Overton for TD
videos.description: Chase Brice lobs it to Diondre Overton for a leaping touchdown as Clemson extends its lead over Wake Forest.
